    <note>Wu(3) Ju(2) [4206] Wife, born Fu(3), died in 1030 at age 82. She was wise and virtuous and could read literature and history. Ju earned the mingjing degree under the Southern Tang and was recruited into the Song bureaucracy by imperial edict in 977 after Southern Tang submitted to Song. Hubei TZ, 23.12b; Ouyang Xiu, WJ, 35.7a-7b. CBD, 2, 1131.</note>
